{"tid":250970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"漁灣邨男子遭襲擊打劫　損失約數十元","createTime":"2017-05-20T13:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T09:28:22.000Z","uid":27601,"like":137,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"305befcdb8a2060c29069364ed46c9c61d7af4d4","tid":250970,"uid":27601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T13:55:03.000Z","msg":"漁灣邨男子遭襲擊打劫　損失約數十元<br />\n2017年05月20日19:07<br />\n<br />\n柴灣漁灣邨發生劫案！一名男子遭人搶走銀包，損失約數十元。<br />\n現場是漁灣邨漁順樓，下午約4時48分，一名中年男子乘搭升降機回家，甫出升降機即遭賊人襲擊，並搶走其銀包。賊人得手後，隨即逃離現場。<br />\n男事主事後報警求助，經初步點算，損失約數十元。他並無受傷，毋須送院。"},{"pid":"d3b91bcd36db9d53cd5b955fda72b6da7e55bf56","tid":250970,"uid":27601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T13:55:44.000Z","msg":"好彩平時帶散紙出街啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19ecc6bf86f9c08100ba2fcf40fb30b0e8d6f992","tid":250970,"uid":81177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T13:56:02.000Z","msg":"史上十大轟動新聞"},{"pid":"eb2e6e115c1f870baa3b307ffce41235a08468b9","tid":250970,"uid":71433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T13:56:06.000Z","msg":"俾人告浪費警力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc14c08aa6ad999c343770d6460271120899b4ab","tid":250970,"uid":42188,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T13:58:59.000Z","msg":"賊人: 屌你老母，男人老狗得幾十蚊係身，抵你住公屋"},{"pid":"cce8a2ac39e3ca24ed398dc9b68026bf50409d1b","tid":250970,"uid":2215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:00:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51b2dbd3e7416bd99bd52bc0d1a7f7ae7b527e79","tid":250970,"uid":2215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T14:01:12.000Z","msg":"諗起細個係差館聽過單案 個賊連砵仔糕都照搶<br />\n俾人拉左罰錢"},{"pid":"9e8564ee2f69e